OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FFormer defence secretary John Healey
OL,7,Fsaid his resignation over the defence
OL,8,Fspending row was "necessary to secure
OL,9,Fthe future of Britain's armed forces".
OL,11,FIn a statement to the House of
OL,12,FCommons, the Labour MP said he stood
OL,13,Fdown with the "very greatest regret
OL,14,Fand reluctance", but was "certain" it
OL,15,Fwas the right decision to leave
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@pD@ROUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
