FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FHe added that he believed the move
OL,7,F"will be seen as necessary in securing
OL,8,Fthe future of our armed forces and our
OL,9,Falliances," and insisted it was "about
OL,10,Four country, not career".
OL,12,FHealey resigned on Thursday following
OL,13,Fa dispute with Sir Keir Starmer over
OL,14,Fmilitary spending, in which he accused
OL,15,Fthe prime minister of making the
OL,16,Fcountry "less safe".
OL,18,FShortly afterwards, Armed Forces
OL,19,FMinister Al Carns also quit over
OL,20,Fconcerns regarding funding for the
OL,21,FDefence Investment Plan (Dip).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FThe prime minister has promised to
OL,7,Fspend 5% of GDP on "national security"
OL,8,Fby 2035, including 3.5% on "core
OL,9,Fdefence".
OL,11,FThe defence investment plan (Dip),
OL,12,Fwhich would set out where the money
OL,13,Fwould come from and how it would be
OL,14,Fspent, was due to be published in the
OL,15,Fautumn, but it has been repeatedly
OL,16,Fdelayed.
OL,18,FThe government has now confirmed that
OL,19,FDip will be released ahead of the Nato
OL,20,Fsummit on July 7.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@fO]pD@\OUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
