PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FPressure has been mounting on the
OL,7,Fprime minister - who is currently
OL,8,Fmeeting G7 leaders in France to
OL,9,Fdiscuss global security - to
OL,10,Faccelerate the increase in defence
OL,11,Fspending.
OL,13,FThe row comes just days before
OL,14,FThursday's crucial Makerfield by-
OL,15,Felection, which could see Andy Burnham
OL,16,Fre-elected to Westminster and go on to
OL,17,Fchallenge Starmer for leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
