PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FDefence spending has long been
OL,7,Fsuggested to be a defining issue for
OL,8,Fthe prime minister, and on Friday,
OL,9,FNumber 10 doubled down on its funding,
OL,10,Fsaying it is the largest increase in
OL,11,Fdefence spending since the Cold War.
OL,13,FIn his first words since resigning,
OL,14,FHealey praised Starmer's defence
OL,15,Fdelivery, saying he "has led this
OL,16,Fdrive, rightly earning respect at home
OL,17,Fand abroad".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FHe went on to commend their work on
OL,7,Fthe commission of the "first of its
OL,8,Fkind, Strategic Defence Review" with a
OL,9,Fvision to transform the UK's armed
OL,10,Fforces.
OL,12,FBut he called on Starmer to now
OL,13,Fimplement "bigger politics, bolder
OL,14,Fpriorities" and said that the PM
OL,15,F"knows what the country needs for
OL,16,Fdefence".
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
