PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FHealey, who served on the Labour
OL,7,Ffrontbenches for more than ten years,
OL,8,Fcriticised the government's plan,
OL,9,Fsaying there is "no date for reaching
OL,10,F3%" spending on defence, and warned
OL,11,Fthat "our adversaries do not follow
OL,12,Ftimetables set by the Treasury".
OL,14,FHe said: "At this dangerous time, I
OL,15,Fsee the current defence investment
OL,16,Fplans falling well short of what is
OL,17,Frequired, a rise at 0.08% from next
OL,18,Fyear to 2030, no date for reaching 3%,
OL,19,Fno path to 3.5%.
OL,26,@rD@CO]sD@FOUtD@_O]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,F"By 2030, well over half of Nato
OL,7,Fmembers will be spending 3% or more.
OL,8,FAnd when allies are looking for
OL,9,FBritish leadership, we must not fall
OL,10,Fbehind.
OL,12,F"When Nato needs European nations to
OL,13,Fstep up, we must not fall short. Our
OL,14,Fadversaries do not follow timetables
OL,15,Fset by the Treasury".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
