CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FThe chief of defence staff, Air Chief
OL,7,FMarshal Sir Richard Knighton, echoed
OL,8,FHealey's words on Tuesday, warning
OL,9,Fthat the armed forces will have to
OL,10,F"dial back" training and operations if
OL,11,Fit does not receive more money.
OL,13,FKnighton told the Lords International
OL,14,FRelations and Defence Committee: "The
OL,15,Fthing that I'm most concerned about is
OL,16,Fthe level of day-to-day activity
OL,17,Ffunding, the resource departmental
OL,18,Fexpenditure limit, because that funds
OL,19,Foperational activity and drives
OL,20,Fexercises and training."
OL,26,@vD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FHe said those activities help with
OL,7,Fpreparedness in the armed forces and
OL,8,Fwarned that without a funding
OL,9,Fincrease, "as John Healey set out,
OL,10,Fthen those areas will come under
OL,11,Fpressure".
OL,13,FHe told the committee that day-to-day
OL,14,Fcosts had soared thanks to inflation,
OL,15,Fpointing to an 88% rise in the cost of
OL,16,Faviation fuel in the past year,
OL,17,Fputting additional "pressure" on the
OL,18,Farmed forces.
OL,26,@yD@TOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
