PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FHealey, now a backbench MP, paid
OL,7,Ftribute to the work of his Cabinet
OL,8,Fcolleagues and said that the funding
OL,9,Ffor defence does not need to be done
OL,10,Fby other cutbacks.
OL,12,F"There are credible ways of meeting
OL,13,Fthe mid-term funding challenges,
OL,14,Fworking multinationally and, as other
OL,15,Fnations in Europe are doing, that
OL,16,Fcould allow us to protect the ability
OL,17,Fto deliver our Labour missions across
OL,18,Fgovernment," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781686099
OL,3,CResignation was 'necessary' to secure
OL,4,Cfuture of armed forces, says Healey
OL,6,FOn national security, Healey suggested
OL,7,Fit is not just a job for defence but
OL,8,Fthat "every department has a part to
OL,9,Fplay in national security and national
OL,10,Fresilience, from energy to transport
OL,11,Fto health".
OL,13,FHe said that security "must run
OL,14,Fthrough the government like letters
OL,15,Fthrough a stick of rock".
OL,17,FHealey said: "I love the job, I won't
OL,18,Fmiss going to bed with three phones or
OL,19,F3am phone calls, and I'm proud of what
OL,20,Fwe've done in less than two years as a
OL,21,FLabour Government."
OL,26,@yD@NOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
